data.description: Charming Centennial Home located on peaceful tree lined street.  Welcome to your dream home! This charming property boasts a plethora of desirable features that make it the perfect place for your family.  Bright ,airy open floor plan, designer title kitchen floor, granite and chef's delight with the new gas cooktop and downdraft vent.  Bonus room with skylights and fireplace for year round enjoyment, wood floors, remodeled bathrooms.  A new furnace and A/C were installed in 2019.  The large back yard is perfect for relaxation and entertaining.  Nestled in a community known for its excellent schools the large back yard is paradise for kids and pets alike, relaxing and entertainment.  This home offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. The updated kitchen and bathrooms showcase the attention to detail and quality of craftsmanship that has gone into maintaining this property. Natural light abounds with an open floor plan and strategically placed windows, natural light fills every corner of this home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  Do you enjoy the great outdoors?  You'll love the convenience of being close to several parks and the Highline Canal.  It's easy to stay active and explore the natural beauty of the area.  This home is a true gem that reflects the pride of ownership.  Meticulously maintained, it's move-in ready and offers the peace of mind that comes with a well-cared-for property, a place to call home where memories are made.
